sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as Developer
    participant PR as Pull Request
    participant Main as main Branch
    participant RP as Release Please
    participant NPM as npm Registry
    participant GH as GitHub Releases
    
    Dev->>PR: Commit with conventional format<br/>(feat:, fix:, etc.)
    PR->>Main: Merge to main
    Main->>RP: Trigger release-please.yml
    
    RP->>RP: Analyze commits since last release
    RP->>RP: Calculate version bump<br/>(major/minor/patch)
    RP->>Main: Create/update Release PR<br/>(version, CHANGELOG.md)
    
    Note over Main,RP: Release PR stays open until<br/>maintainer is ready to release
    
    Dev->>RP: Merge Release PR
    RP->>RP: Detect release_created=true
    
    par Parallel Publishing
        RP->>NPM: Job: npm-publish<br/>npm ci, build, test, publish
        RP->>GH: Job: build-extension<br/>npm ci, build, mcpb pack
    end
    
    NPM-->>RP: Package published with provenance
    GH-->>RP: .mcpb file uploaded to release